      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "STORM HUSTLER (1) is a consistent runner who is having his first look at course. Last start winner off a middle draw scoring by 2 lengths at Warragul over 460m (25.95). Some good form is emerging from his last run. Great chance to get the job done again. REANNA'S PRIDE (8) is first up since finishing sixth (30.42) in a Grade 5 at The Meadows over 525m four-and-a-half months ago. Has never been out of the money in three starts this course and distance. Has a good overall strike-rate and can find the frame here. PEPPER RUSH (4) had a tough draw to overcome and was game in defeat when only 2 lengths from Jetstream Icon in second (23.94) at this track. Consistent performer from this draw with a win and two minor placings to his credit. Ready to find winning form. MEPUNGA SCARLETT (5) boasts a solid strike-rate over this trip.",
